  "name": "extend: first EXTEND on a Checked In booking pushes Check Out out, notifies owner once, sets the notified flag (B12/F21)",
  "comment": "LOCKED 16 July: guests can extend repeatedly (uncapped); owner is notified on the FIRST extension only. Overnight extension increment is +1 day, so Check Out 2026-07-22T08:00Z becomes 2026-07-23T08:00Z. Checkout Warning Sent At is cleared to re-arm the cron for the new window; Extension Owner Notified is set true so later extensions do not re-notify.",
  "seed": {
